{"tid":202690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞視記者採訪反水貨客遊行「中椒」 警查兩年：濫權投訴證明屬實","createTime":"2017-04-15T16:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T23:36:24.000Z","uid":43189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20defd2ea0558eb45f5b1294ef9ed17a41559bcb","tid":202690,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170415/large/1492227384_d797.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170415%2Flarge%2F1492227384_d797.jpg&h=b7a038a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前亞視記者江川2015年3月在元朗採訪反水貨客示威期間，雖然手持亞視咪牌，但仍被在場軍裝警員近距離向他面部噴胡椒噴霧，之後更被襲擊。江川事後投訴警員濫權，投訴警察課經過兩年調查，近日回覆他稱涉案警員濫用職權的指控已列作「證明屬實」。<br />\n<br />\n投訴警察課又指，涉案的警員事發後未有按照規定，盡快向上級匯報事件，亦被列作「未經舉報但證明屬實」，江川引述警方稱將向該名警員採取適當的紀律行動。<br />\n<br />\n事發在2015年3月1號，江川到元朗採訪反水貨客遊行，隨遊行隊伍轉入壽富街時，警員指現場有人衝擊警方防線，有站在鐵馬後警員手持胡椒噴霧向江川面部近距離噴射，除江川以外，亦有一名有線電視記者被噴中。警方事後就指當時情況混亂，射中記者可能是意外。今次並非江川首次被警員襲擊，他2014年9月28日在政府總部採訪市民衝入公民廣場時，亦被在場警員「叉頸」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170415/56567599\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170415%2F56567599&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=1a0c95f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170415%2F56567599&h=e9df92a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170415/56567599</a>"},{"pid":"b8dde68aee94f3a15b1ac917bbd16b8766e42cd2","tid":202690,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f1e261454b7e95c7990372d90dd9a8e32fda44","tid":202690,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:57:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c884c24176435df1d5cc1bd29ee0b2dd2e71e85","tid":202690,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T23:36:24.000Z","msg":"紀律行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼告埋上法庭"}]}